Package AddressBookApplication

Class AddressBook

java.lang.Object
AddressBookApplication.AddressBook
public class AddressBook
extends java.lang.Object
This Class holds a collection of objects of AddressEntry class. This class contains an inner class SortLn which overrides the comparator class's compare() method. used to sort elements based on lastName field. contains a List method that lists all the elements in the container. contains an add method for adding to the list. contains a find method that finds elements. contains a remove method for removing elements. contains a sort method for Sorting the Address Book based on last Names.
Author:
parsia fatoorechi.
